==Hindi==
===Demonstrative pronoun===
'''उन''' (un)

# [[those]] ([[oblique]] case only, see below for direct. Singular: [[उस]])
#:उन मकानों [[में]] [[छह]] कमरे हैं — ''In those houses there are six rooms.'' (lit., "these houses in six rooms are")
# [[him]] (oblique case only, far reference, polite. If no additional [[respect]] is conveyed, [[उस]] is used)
#:उनको [[पैसे]] [[देना|दे]] [[दो]] — ''Give money to him.'' (lit., "him to money give")
# [[her]] (oblique case only, far reference. If no additional [[respect]] is conveyed, [[उस]] is used)
#:उनको पैसे दे दो — ''Give money to her.''
# [[it]] (oblique case only).

====Inflection====
[[Direct]]: [[वे]]
Direct, singular, far reference: [[वह]] (vah) — [[that]]

